1
00:00:16,683 --> 00:00:19,379
My name is Mary Alice Young.
我叫Mary Alice Young。

2
00:00:19,452 --> 00:00:22,444
In this morning's paper, you may come across an article
在今天早上的论文中，您可能会遇到一篇文章

3
00:00:22,555 --> 00:00:25,888
about the unusual day I had last week.
关于我上周经历的不寻常的一天

4
00:00:25,959 --> 00:00:29,486
Normally, there's never anything newsworthy about my life,
通常，关于我的生活，没有任何新闻值得报道，

5
00:00:29,562 --> 00:00:32,395
but that all changed last Thursday.
但这一切都在上周四发生了变化。

6
00:00:32,465 --> 00:00:36,196
Of course, everything seemed quite normal at first.
当然，起初一切似乎都很正常。

7
00:00:36,269 --> 00:00:38,100
I made breakfast for my family.
我为家人做早餐。

8
00:00:40,106 --> 00:00:42,301
I performed my chores.
我做了家务。

9
00:00:43,777 --> 00:00:46,507
I completed my projects.
我完成了我的项目。

10
00:00:47,547 --> 00:00:50,141
I ran my errands.
我跑腿了。

11
00:00:50,216 --> 00:00:54,448
In truth, I spent the day as I spent every other day,
说实话，我每天都过着一天，

12
00:00:54,521 --> 00:01:00,892
quietly polishing the routine of my life until it gleamed with perfection.
悄悄地磨光我的生活，直到完美地闪闪发光。

13
00:01:03,196 --> 00:01:07,929
That's why it was so astonishing when I decided to go to my hallway closet
这就是为什么当我决定去我的走廊壁橱时是如此令人惊讶的原因

14
00:01:08,034 --> 00:01:12,767
and retrieve a revolver that had never been used.
并取回从未使用过的左轮手枪。

15
00:01:17,177 --> 00:01:21,671
My body was discovered by my neighbor, Mrs. Martha Huber,
我的尸体是由邻居玛莎·胡伯夫人发现的，